msgid "# Update-ClusterVirtualMachineConfiguration"
msgstr "# 更新集群虚拟机配置"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Refreshes the configuration of a clustered virtual machine within a failover"
" cluster."
msgstr "刷新故障转移集群中集群虚拟机的配置。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The `Update-ClusterVirtualMachineConfiguration` cmdlet refreshes the configuration of a clustered\n"
"virtual machine within a failover cluster. Use this cmdlet if a hardware device, such as a network\n"
"adapter, is to be added or removed or the hardware configuration settings, such as the setting for\n"
"virtual memory, are being changed for a clustered virtual machine."
msgstr ""
"`Update-ClusterVirtualMachineConfiguration` 这个 cmdlet "
"用于更新故障转移集群中集群化虚拟机的配置。当需要添加或删除某个硬件设备（例如网络适配器），或者需要更改该集群化虚拟机的硬件配置设置（例如虚拟内存设置）时，可以使用此"
" cmdlet。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid ""
"### Example 1: Refresh a clustered virtual machine on the local cluster"
msgstr "### 示例 1：刷新本地集群中的集群化虚拟机"

msgid ""
"This example refreshes the clustered virtual machine named `Virtual Machine Configuration VM1` on\n"
"the local cluster."
msgstr "这个示例会刷新本地集群中名为“Virtual Machine Configuration VM1”的集群化虚拟机。"

msgid "### Example 2: Refresh a clustered virtual machine on a cluster"
msgstr "### 示例 2：刷新集群中的虚拟机"

msgid ""
"This example refreshes the clustered virtual machine named `Virtual Machine Configuration VM2` on\n"
"the cluster named `cluster1`. The example uses splatting to pass parameter values from\n"
"the `$Parameters` variable to the command. Learn more about\n"
"[Splatting](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting)."
msgstr ""
"这个示例会刷新名为 `Virtual Machine Configuration VM2` 的集群虚拟机，该虚拟机位于名为 `cluster1` "
"的集群中。示例使用了 “Splatting” 技术，将参数值从 `$Parameters` 变量传递给相应的命令。有关 "
"[Splatting](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting)"
" 的更多信息，请参阅相关文档。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定要运行此cmdlet的集群名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.`或被省略，则cmdlet将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid "Specifies the clustered virtual machine resource to update."
msgstr "指定要更新的集群化虚拟机资源。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the clustered virtual machine resource to update."
msgstr "指定要更新的集群化虚拟机资源的名称。"

msgid "Specifies the virtual machine identifier (ID)."
msgstr "指定虚拟机的标识符（ID）。"

